Distribution:
China
(
Guangxi
). Known only from the cave Dalongguan Dong (
Fig. 11
). This cave is very close to the village Dalongguan. With a very small and narrow entrance (
Fig. 12A
), then the passage becomes much wider. It is about two hundred meters long before joining an underground river. All of the beetles were discovered and collected in a wet area about four to five dozen meters from the entrance (
Fig. 12 B, C
).
